1
00:00:30,970 --> 00:00:33,250
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,270 --> 00:00:36,210
[Episode 11
Half Demon Bitter Fruit]

3
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,920
Th-th-this...

4
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:58,400
You thought hiding your aura

5
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:00,550
could fool me?

6
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,760
Your concern betrays you.

7
00:01:02,860 --> 00:01:05,180
Little raccoon. Tell me the truth.

8
00:01:10,850 --> 00:01:12,750
My Lady,
there's no need to beat around the bush.

9
00:01:12,750 --> 00:01:13,870
I killed them.

10
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:19,530
I've wanted to kill those three
for a long time.

11
00:01:19,530 --> 00:01:21,970
They lorded it over the academy
all day long.

12
00:01:21,970 --> 00:01:22,850
Not just Li Mao,

13
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:23,940
who in this academy

14
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:25,539
hasn't been bullied by them?

15
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:27,870
Wang Renjie wanted to pass
the imperial exams with top honors.

16
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:28,930
If he actually did,

17
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,560
and became an official someday,

18
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,560
now that would be true injustice.

19
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,509
No one cared,

20
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:37,640
but I did.

21
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,560
Tell me in detail,

22
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,700
how did you kill the three of them,

23
00:01:42,789 --> 00:01:45,120
and where did you hide the bodies?

24
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:47,120
I waited until they were dead drunk,

25
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,050
strangled them,

26
00:01:48,420 --> 00:01:50,140
then tore off their arms,

27
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,940
and hung the bodies from the rafters.

28
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:54,979
Where did you hide their arms?

29
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,840
Search every corner carefully.

30
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,360
Don't overlook a single clue.

31
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,130
Not just Li Mao,

32
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,300
who in this academy

33
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:12,930
hasn't been bullied by them?

34
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,010
Wang Renjie wanted to pass
the imperial exams with top honors.

35
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:16,170
If he actually did,

36
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,110
and became an official someday,

37
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:20,300
now that would be true injustice.

38
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:22,650
Found them!

39
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,630
My Lord,
six arms were recovered from the well,

40
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:29,560
matching the wounds on the bodies.

41
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:08,840
The severed arms of Wang Renjie
and the other two have been found.

42
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,150
How much longer will you stay silent?

43
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:28,000
My Lord, I killed Wang Renjie.

44
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,490
You killed him?

45
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,150
Yes.

46
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:32,850
Okay.

47
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,160
Then tell me in detail,

48
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:37,750
where did you hide the severed arms?

49
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,280
I threw them away.

50
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,310
Where did you throw them?

51
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,160
I just threw them anywhere.

52
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:47,930
You don't know,

53
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:51,510
because you weren't the one
who hid those arms.

54
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,340
But someone else does.

55
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:55,329
Ji has already confessed.

56
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:58,160
He put the severed arms in the dry well.

57
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,470
At this point,

58
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,280
lying is useless.

59
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,310
Think carefully,

60
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:08,150
what did you see that night,

61
00:04:11,010 --> 00:04:13,360
and what are you hiding?

62
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:22,300
That night, I did return to the academy.

63
00:04:23,050 --> 00:04:26,110
I wanted to get some books
to study in the ruined temple.

64
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,630
Spare us!

65
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,040
We were wrong!

66
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,480
We'll never do it again!

67
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,140
Remember what you said today.

68
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,440
If I ever find out

69
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:40,440
that you dare to harm a single hair
on Li Mao's head,

70
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:41,960
I will come back

71
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:43,920
and tear off every pair of your hands

72
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:46,560
that you only use to bully the weak.

73
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:47,810
We were wrong!

74
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:51,770
I'll let you taste
what it's like to lose your limbs.

75
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,280
Spare us!

76
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:01,310
Ji.

77
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,970
Look at yourself.

78
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:10,510
You're neither human

79
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,430
nor demon.

80
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:16,160
You deserve to be trampled
underfoot by others.

81
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:16,890
If I were you,

82
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:20,820
I'd have bashed my head
against the academy gates long ago.

83
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:24,020
It would be better than letting
your mother see you like this,

84
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:27,210
so she wouldn't have to
worry over you day and night.

85
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,510
Ji. Ji.

86
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,070
I...

87
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,190
Ji...

88
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,510
I beg you,

89
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:38,370
please tell my mother for me again

90
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:39,770
that I'm reviewing my lessons.

91
00:05:39,770 --> 00:05:40,300
Get lost!

92
00:05:40,890 --> 00:05:43,290
Go kneel
and tell your own mother yourself!

93
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:44,720
I know.

94
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,090
Ji was just disappointed in me,

95
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:49,490
that's why he said those harsh words.

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,659
That night,

97
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:54,000
my mind was a tangled mess.

98
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,730
I had no mood to review my lessons.

99
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,530
So I bought some wine

100
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,920
and went to the ruined temple.

101
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,560
I never left after that,

102
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,480
until dawn when I went to school.

103
00:06:07,540 --> 00:06:08,870
But I arrived too early.

104
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:10,830
I was a bit tired,

105
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,880
so I fell asleep outside the academy.

106
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:26,120
Are you on good terms with Ji?

107
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:29,540
Ji likes to keep to himself.

108
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:33,070
He keeps a cold distance

109
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,380
from everyone in the academy.

110
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,720
He and I

111
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:39,750
barely ever spoke to each other.

112
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:42,310
Except,

113
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:47,090
when Wang Renjie broke my leg,

114
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,530
I asked him to deliver a message

115
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,630
to my family.

116
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:54,159
After that,

117
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:57,150
we've only spoken twice.

118
00:06:57,710 --> 00:06:58,950
When did you meet him?

119
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:02,240
Sometime between 7 and 8 PM.

120
00:07:06,450 --> 00:07:08,570
Do you have anything else to say?

121
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:15,640
On my way to the ruined temple,

122
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:20,080
I came across a scholar.

123
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,550
He asked me for a bowl of wine,

124
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:26,400
so I invited him to the temple with me.

125
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,960
Do you remember what he looked like?

126
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,380
I really can't remember his face.

127
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:34,100
I only remember

128
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,830
he was dressed in white.

129
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,360
In the moonlight,

130
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,040
he seemed to be glowing.

131
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:46,920
Then

132
00:07:47,330 --> 00:07:48,170
can he prove

133
00:07:48,210 --> 00:07:50,750
that you stayed in the ruined temple
the whole time?

134
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:51,190
Yes.

135
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,740
He definitely can.

136
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,550
That day, I shared my wine with him.

137
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,070
Later...

138
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,070
Later I got drunk.

139
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,440
He also rested in the temple.

140
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,100
With him there,

141
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:06,640
he can definitely prove
that I was in the temple all night.

142
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,190
In that case,

143
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:11,150
then think carefully about his appearance

144
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:12,360
and draw him out.

145
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,920
Once we find him,

146
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,220
you will be cleared of suspicion.

147
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,190
My Lord.

148
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:25,070
I will do my best.

149
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,360
But My Lord,

150
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,950
I have one more request.

151
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:31,160
Could you go to my home

152
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:33,750
and tell my mother I'm safe?

153
00:08:34,909 --> 00:08:35,440
Alright.

154
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:43,030
Lord Bai,
why not return to the county yamen first

155
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,720
and interrogate Ji thoroughly?

156
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:47,550
I'll go and reassure
that Tiger Spirit's mother

157
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,750
in your stead.

158
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:49,630
No.

159
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,080
Why not?

160
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:54,910
Lady Fufeng, you look unwell.

161
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,360
Your spiritual power must not have
fully recovered yet.

162
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,630
I'd better stay by your side at all times.

163
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:06,440
Lord Bai truly has a healer's heart.

164
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:11,930
I have some questions
to ask Auntie Li in person.

165
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:15,000
Besides, there is one more thing
I don't understand.

166
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,750
Humans and demons have coexisted
in Yin-Yang Crossing for centuries.

167
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,630
Are demons here

168
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:21,390
always looked down upon by humans?

169
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,940
Li Mao is looked down upon,

170
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:26,660
not because he is a demon,

171
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:29,920
but because he is a half-demon.

172
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:34,400
The human world values clans and surnames,

173
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:37,820
while demons honor bloodline and heritage.

174
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,520
Caught in between,

175
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,420
half-demons have too weak demonic power

176
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:44,750
to protect themselves,

177
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:47,630
and are more sensitive than humans.

178
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,150
That's why ancient books record

179
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,570
a ban in Yin-Yang Crossing,

180
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:55,590
forbidding marriage
between humans and demons.

181
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:58,040
The law may restrict actions,

182
00:09:58,750 --> 00:10:00,610
but how can it restrict the heart?

183
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,870
Yet this sincere devotion

184
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:06,540
only bears bitter fruit in the end,

185
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,360
which the child must bear alone.

186
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:13,150
So Li Mao is that bitter fruit.

187
00:10:26,890 --> 00:10:27,840
Aunt Li.

188
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,000
Aunt Li.

189
00:11:18,540 --> 00:11:21,660
There are no signs of struggle
in the yard or the house,

190
00:11:22,450 --> 00:11:24,480
and the lock wasn't forced.

191
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:27,030
It seems that an acquaintance visited,

192
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:29,030
and Mrs. Li opened the door herself.

193
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,090
Lady Fufeng.

194
00:11:32,690 --> 00:11:33,480
If so,

195
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,790
from the academy to the Li residence,

196
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,790
how long does it take at the fastest?

197
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:39,050
For an ordinary human,

198
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,630
going through the West Street

199
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,630
and taking alleys to avoid the market,

200
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:44,160
it takes an hour at the fastest.

201
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,070
For a demon,

202
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,170
it would be even faster.

203
00:11:49,430 --> 00:11:51,860
Aunt Li's time of death was

204
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:55,630
between 10 and 11 PM last night,

205
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:59,280
almost the same time
as Wang Renjie and the others.

206
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:01,960
After striking at the academy,

207
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,490
the killer didn't stop at all.

208
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:04,870
He went straight to the destination,

209
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:06,730
barely pausing to catch a breath.

210
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:19,530
Hu.

211
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:20,910
My Lord.

212
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:23,940
Master.

213
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:27,770
Li Mao's detailed household
registration has been retrieved.

214
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:33,870
Li Mao,

215
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:35,500
half-demon and half-human,

216
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:36,960
was registered in Yin-Yang Crossing.

217
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,020
His mother, Li Yun,

218
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:40,600
was a local washerwoman
in Yin-Yang Crossing.

219
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,930
His father, Mao Da, a Tiger Spirit

220
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:45,230
used to be a street performer.

221
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:47,100
He was abducted
into a wealthy merchant's mansion,

222
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:50,010
forced to perform limb severing
for entertainment,

223
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:53,290
finally died after a banquet
where he was cut nine times,

224
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:56,450
and his body was abandoned
in the wilderness.

225
00:12:57,450 --> 00:12:58,020
My Lady.

226
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,840
Lady Fufeng.

227
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:02,790
My Lord.

228
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,630
Aunt Zhang witnessed last night

229
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:07,390
that Li Mao returned home.

230
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:09,850
Answering your honor,

231
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,270
I got up to empty
the chamber pot last night,

232
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:14,730
and I clearly saw Li Mao
knocking at the door.

233
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,150
When?

234
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:17,310
I got up during the Second Watch,

235
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,060
just as the night watchman
passed by my door.

236
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:22,010
That would be 9:45 PM, wouldn't it?

237
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,840
Are you sure it was Li Mao?

238
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,720
He wore Qiuzhi Academy's uniform robe.

239
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:29,010
who else could it be?

240
00:13:33,410 --> 00:13:34,790
Did he have a severed arm?

241
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:37,000
I didn't notice that.

242
00:13:38,330 --> 00:13:39,390
If he had both arms,

243
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,940
it doesn't make sense.

244
00:14:15,910 --> 00:14:16,670
My Lords,

245
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,640
Have you delivered
my message to my mother?

246
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,920
We told her you're helping with the case,

247
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:24,820
and everything is fine.

248
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:26,420
So she doesn't need to worry.

249
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:30,720
Good.

250
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:33,270
Li Mao.

251
00:14:34,310 --> 00:14:36,390
You often study late at the academy.

252
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:39,600
Your mother must leave the door
unlocked for you, right?

253
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,200
Yes.

254
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:41,860
My mother

255
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:44,860
always leaves it unlocked
for me every night.

256
00:14:46,730 --> 00:14:48,130
You're also a filial son.

257
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,730
I suppose when you go back,

258
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:51,430
you wouldn't knock loudly,

259
00:14:51,810 --> 00:14:54,010
for fear of disturbing her rest, right?

260
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:56,640
My mother works hard
washing clothes during the day.

261
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:57,720
I dare not wake her,

262
00:14:58,580 --> 00:15:00,850
so I always slip in quietly.

263
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:10,400
Lady Fufeng.

264
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:14,440
Once Li Mao's drawing is finished,

265
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:17,100
please send it
to the county yamen immediately.

266
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:20,740
Lord Bai, you certainly gives me orders

267
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,590
quite naturally now.

268
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,280
Please, Lady Fufeng.

269
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:25,610
The case is urgent.

270
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:29,210
I must return to the county yamen
to interrogate Ji immediately.

271
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:38,130
My Lady, what's wrong?

272
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,780
You need spiritual power?

273
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:41,800
With a fever this high,

274
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,250
haven't you even noticed it yourself?

275
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,840
It's been a long time since I got sick.

276
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:50,900
I didn't even know.

277
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:53,080
After I finish interrogating Ji,

278
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,480
I'll take some medicine.

279
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:01,900
Th-this is...

280
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,660
A little magic arts

281
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,270
will suppress your illness temporarily,

282
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:07,930
but it'll only last half a day.

283
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:11,170
If you don't rest after tonight's work...

284
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,440
What will happen?

285
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:15,830
Then you'll just stay sick.

286
00:16:19,670 --> 00:16:20,730
Thank you, My Lady.

287
00:16:25,370 --> 00:16:25,830
My Lady,

288
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,840
that magic arts just now,

289
00:16:27,850 --> 00:16:29,010
can you do it again?

290
00:16:29,290 --> 00:16:31,620
It would be great
if it could last for a day.

291
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:36,510
Then you will die on the spot.

292
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,810
Is that good?

293
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,320
No, no, no.

294
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:43,330
Thank you, My Lady.

295
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,240
Master.

296
00:16:56,210 --> 00:16:59,070
You've been spending day
and night with him lately.

297
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:01,320
You finally built up some spiritual power

298
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,580
to nurture your heart.

299
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:03,270
And now,

300
00:17:03,990 --> 00:17:06,119
you've given it all back to him at once.

301
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:12,599
It's just adding a handful of fodder

302
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:14,150
to a working draft horse.

303
00:17:14,829 --> 00:17:16,020
If he runs faster,

304
00:17:16,930 --> 00:17:18,660
the case will be solved faster.

305
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:20,000
For me,

306
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:21,920
and for Yin-Yang Crossing,

307
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,920
it's a good thing.

308
00:17:43,410 --> 00:17:45,370
Ji, that night between 9 and 11 PM,

309
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:48,340
after you killed Wang Renjie
and the others,

310
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:49,420
where did you go?

311
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,530
You went to Li Mao's house.

312
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:13,520
Who's there?

313
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:14,480
Auntie Li,

314
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:16,000
it's me, Ji.

315
00:18:18,310 --> 00:18:19,240
Li Mao...

316
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,650
He was studying in the academy.

317
00:18:21,650 --> 00:18:23,200
It got too late, so he stayed there.

318
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,400
He asked me to tell you

319
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:25,300
not to worry.

320
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:26,550
I see.

321
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,770
Thank you for your trouble.

322
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,680
I...

323
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,400
According to Li Mao,

324
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,470
the two of you barely spoke,

325
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:40,960
only a few words total.

326
00:18:41,650 --> 00:18:43,040
Why would you go this far

327
00:18:43,130 --> 00:18:44,370
for him?

328
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:46,080
Delivering messages,

329
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:46,790
and even

330
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,480
killing for him?

331
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:50,950
Because of Auntie Li,

332
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:55,270
she is my benefactor.

333
00:18:57,330 --> 00:18:57,960
Back then,

334
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:02,410
I was just a stray kitten
without much intelligence.

335
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,490
How can such a skinny kitten

336
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:05,880
survive this winter?

337
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:08,000
Are you starving?

338
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:10,440
Did your mother leave before teaching you

339
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:11,240
to catch mice?

340
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:15,930
The master doesn't like pets.

341
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:17,680
I don't have a home

342
00:19:18,090 --> 00:19:19,330
of my own either.

343
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:26,720
That year, some bullies caught me,

344
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,600
tied a rope around me,

345
00:19:29,090 --> 00:19:31,220
and dragged me along the river for fun.

346
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,650
It was Auntie Li.

347
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:35,840
She was still unmarried then,

348
00:19:36,370 --> 00:19:38,280
just a petite, delicate girl.

349
00:19:38,990 --> 00:19:40,720
She rushed up to argue with them

350
00:19:41,110 --> 00:19:42,310
and snatched me away.

351
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,420
She bandaged my wounds

352
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,200
and gave me food.

353
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,760
Fearing her family was too poor

354
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:51,770
to raise me well,

355
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:53,510
she begged others

356
00:19:53,850 --> 00:19:55,760
to send me to a wealthy family.

357
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,800
That I have survived to this day,

358
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,550
cultivated a human form,

359
00:20:00,550 --> 00:20:01,880
and learned to read and write,

360
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:04,540
is all thanks to Auntie Li's
kindness back then.

361
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,480
That time,

362
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:06,960
Li Mao asked me

363
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:08,880
to deliver a message to his family.

364
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:10,010
May I ask who you are?

365
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:12,340
I recognized her at first glance.

366
00:20:12,390 --> 00:20:13,570
Over these thirty years,

367
00:20:13,570 --> 00:20:14,530
she has aged a lot,

368
00:20:14,530 --> 00:20:15,720
but it's definitely her.

369
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,650
I can't be wrong.

370
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:17,880
I am Ji.

371
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,070
So,

372
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,400
you are not the murderer.

373
00:20:33,110 --> 00:20:34,200
Everything you did

374
00:20:34,470 --> 00:20:36,800
was just to take the blame for Li Mao

375
00:20:37,330 --> 00:20:39,810
to repay Auntie Li's kindness.

376
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:44,790
What are you talking about, My Lord?

377
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:46,240
I killed them.

378
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:49,070
What do you mean by taking the blame?

379
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:54,230
This is my deduction

380
00:20:54,330 --> 00:20:56,410
of what happened that night.

381
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:59,040
You sneaked into the academy

382
00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:01,830
and taught Wang Renjie
and the other two a lesson,

383
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:03,310
hoping to scare them,

384
00:21:03,890 --> 00:21:05,850
so they'd never bully Li Mao again.

385
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:08,110
And later,

386
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:10,920
you ran into Li Mao outside the academy.

387
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,240
You spoke harshly to him.

388
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:14,880
It seemed like humiliation,

389
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:17,790
but was actually frustration
that he wouldn't stand up for himself.

390
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:19,720
You hoped he would rise up because of this

391
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:21,090
and learn to protect himself.

392
00:21:21,090 --> 00:21:23,760
You couldn't bear it in the end,

393
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:27,110
and still went to reassure
Auntie Li for him.

394
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:29,160
But you never expected

395
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:31,750
that after Wang Renjie
and the others died,

396
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:32,550
you believed

397
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,920
that Li Mao was provoked by your words

398
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,380
to commit a grave mistake,

399
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:39,310
so you took the murder charge

400
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,790
on yourself.

401
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:44,950
If I didn't kill them,

402
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:46,550
how would I know

403
00:21:46,550 --> 00:21:48,620
that the six severed arms were hidden
in the abandoned well?

404
00:21:48,620 --> 00:21:50,550
Isn't this irrefutable evidence?

405
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:54,680
Cat demons

406
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:57,330
are born with a keen sense of smell.

407
00:21:57,590 --> 00:21:59,650
The fresh smell of blood from the well

408
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:02,400
could be easily detected by you.

409
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:05,260
This doesn't prove
that you are the killer.

410
00:22:07,030 --> 00:22:07,680
I am

411
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,790
the one who killed them.

412
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:10,240
Fine.

413
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,880
What about Auntie Li?

414
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,800
That woman who showed you kindness,

415
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:15,270
and gave you a new life,

416
00:22:15,710 --> 00:22:16,920
could you really be so heartless

417
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:18,780
as to kill her with your own hands?

418
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,440
Auntie Li?

419
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:33,720
She...

420
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,200
She was killed?

421
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:43,590
Ji,

422
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:44,970
get up first.

423
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:48,680
Ji,

424
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:50,930
listen to me.

425
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:52,630
I have determined

426
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:54,960
that Li Mao is definitely not the killer.

427
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:57,360
There is no way
he would kill his own mother.

428
00:22:58,030 --> 00:22:59,760
You two covered for each other.

429
00:23:00,050 --> 00:23:01,780
Your sincerity was misplaced,

430
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,240
which instead delayed

431
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,640
finding the real killer.

432
00:23:05,450 --> 00:23:07,000
You need to be strong now.

433
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:08,830
Think carefully.

434
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:10,160
Think carefully.

435
00:23:10,610 --> 00:23:13,090
Are there any other details
or strange things

436
00:23:13,090 --> 00:23:14,490
that you have forgotten?

437
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,650
Strange things?

438
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:19,930
If

439
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:22,370
I had to say there was something strange,

440
00:23:24,090 --> 00:23:26,030
after I delivered the message that day,

441
00:23:26,030 --> 00:23:27,240
I saw a person.

442
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:29,780
That person

443
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:31,850
was dressed in white,

444
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,900
looked like a scholar,

445
00:23:34,510 --> 00:23:36,040
and had a very strange aura.

446
00:23:36,550 --> 00:23:38,200
On my way to the ruined temple,

447
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,920
I came across a scholar.

448
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:41,550
He was dressed in white.

449
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:44,510
In the moonlight,

450
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:47,080
he seemed to be glowing.

451
00:23:47,510 --> 00:23:48,560
A scholar in white.

